import React from 'react';
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'
import { LinkContainer } from 'react-router-bootstrap'

function Header() {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" expand="sm">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand href="#">DRINK THE DIRT</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Collapse>
          <Nav>
            <Nav.Link href="/">
              <LinkContainer to="/">Home</LinkContainer>
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="/coffee">
              <LinkContainer to="/coffee">Coffee</LinkContainer>
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="/brewing">Brewing</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="/classes">Tastings & Classes</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="/about">About</Nav.Link>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Header;
